author: @kennewton2049
comment: Joslin every morning I throw my ear buds in and listen to whatever comes up on my You Tube feed.  I subscribe to several feeds, yours being one of them. As soon as this started, I knew it had to be you and Emily.  This is, and always will be one of my all-time favorite songs.  The last time I heard it sung was at my daughter's Covid wedding in North Carolina which ended up being in her backyard with 30 close friends and family.  Interestingly enough, one of the most beautiful weddings I have ever attended.  Today, when this came on, I stopped in my tracks and listened to every note.  This is perfect in every way.  Thank you for sharing your gift, and for taking me this morning on a trip down memory lane.  Nancy
